# Testing

## Stack (configured — do not restate)

- Runner: `bun:test` — see [`bunfig.toml`](../../bunfig.toml) preload
- Preset: [`tools/tests-preset`](../../tools/tests-preset) — HappyDOM, Testing Library, cleanup
- Details: [`tools/tests-preset/AGENTS.md`](../../tools/tests-preset/AGENTS.md)

## Naming and structure

- `describe('<module> - <unit>', () => {})`
- `it('<expected outcome> when <condition>', () => {})`
- No inline comments or JSDoc in tests; names document behavior
- AAA layout; blank line between logical groups inside a test

## Quality bar

- Assert observable behavior, not internals
- One failure reason per test; no flakiness (mock time/network/random)
- Mock **boundaries** only (network, DB, fs, env) — not pure logic
- Restore spies; preset handles most cleanup

## File placement

- Unit: `src/<area>/<thing>.test.ts` or `src/__tests__/`
- Integration: `src/__tests__/<thing>.integration.test.ts`

## Patterns

- Table-driven cases via `cases.forEach` or `test.each` (Bun: `test.each` / `describe.each`, not `it.each`)

## Commands

See [`docs/CHEATSHEET.md`](../../docs/CHEATSHEET.md) — `bun test`, `bun run overall`.
